  "444": "Item for: Eevee Protects against weather damage. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Eevee.",
  "445": "Item for: Vaporeon May afflict attacking enemies with a Cringe status condition. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Vaporeon.",
  "446": "Item for: Jolteon May afflict attacking enemies with a Paralysis status condition. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Jolteon.",
  "447": "Item for: Flareon May afflict attacking enemies with a Burn status condition. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Flareon.",
  "448": "Item for: Espeon May afflict attacking enemies with a Confused status condition. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Espeon.",
  "449": "Item for: Umbreon May afflict attacking enemies with a Blinker status, which obscures vision. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Umbreon.",
  "450": "Item for: Leafeon May afflict attacking enemies with a Poisoned status, a Paralysis status, or a Sleep status. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Leafeon. You can get a Virid Collar at the Croagunk Swap Shop by swapping: Eevee Tail, Eevee Card and Evolve Charm. That's the easy way! An item with a -rarity rating is very hard to get. It's beyond valuable!",
  "451": "Item for: Glaceon May afflict attacking enemies with a Frozen status condition. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Glaceon.",
  "452": "Item for: Tyrogue Earns the Pokémon Exp. Points every time it takes damage. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Tyrogue.",
  "453": "Item for: Hitmonlee Makes the Pokémon counterstrike against Physical Attacks, inflicting the same damage on an attacker. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Hitmonlee.",
  "454": "Item for: Hitmonchan May seal one of an enemy's known moves when it attacks the Pokémon. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Hitmonchan.",
  "455": "Item for: Hitmontop Enables the Pokémon to ignore the effects of an enemy's Reflect and Light Screen when attacking. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Hitmontop.",
  "456": "Item for: Pichu Enables the occasional use of a move with no PP consumption. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Pichu.",
  "457": "Item for: Cleffa Raises the chances of finding treasure after defeating enemies. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Cleffa.",
  "458": "Item for: Igglybuff Raises the chances of finding treasure after defeating enemies. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Igglybuff.",
  "459": "Item for: Togepi Makes the Pokémon bounce a thrown or hurled item back. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Togepi.",
  "460": "Item for: Tyrogue Enables the Pokémon to deal full damage to Ghost-type enemies using Normal- and Fighting-type moves. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Tyrogue.",
  "461": "Item for: Smoochum Enables the Pokémon to deal full damage to Dark-type enemies using Psychic-type moves. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Smoochum.",
  "462": "Item for: Elekid Boosts the Pokémon's maximum HP. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Elekid.",
  "463": "Item for: Magby Boosts the Pokémon's maximum HP. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Magby.",
  "464": "Item for: Azurill Boosts the Pokémon's maximum HP. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Azurill.",
  "465": "Item for: Wynaut Raises the chances of finding treasure after defeating enemies. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Wynaut.",
